  "text": "One specific advantage of this model is that it allows the agent through its actions (and predictions) to optimize not just its policy but also potentially the physical device on which its policy is computed. [CITATION_1] An additional advantage is that there is no need anymore for a time parametert, since it is the environment that determines how much computation the agent is allowed.",
